```plantuml
@startuml boot2podman_machine

actor User
participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "Libmachine" as Libmachine
participant "Driver (e.g., VirtualBox)" as Driver
participant "Provisioner (e.g., Boot2Podman)" as Provisioner
participant "VM" as VM

User -> CLI: podman-machine create --driver=virtualbox
CLI -> Libmachine: createHost(driver="virtualbox")
Libmachine -> Driver: Create()
Driver -> VM: Start VM
VM --> Driver: VM Running
Driver --> Libmachine: Success
Libmachine -> Provisioner: Provision()
Provisioner -> VM: Install Podman (via SSH)
VM --> Provisioner: Podman Installed
Provisioner --> Libmachine: Success
Libmachine --> CLI: Host Created
CLI --> User: Machine Ready

@enduml
```